Sports Cabinet Minister Amina Mohamed has issued a passionate appeal, especially to politicians, to stay away from the 7pm match which Harambee Stars need to winAfter Harambee Stars' last home match against Comoros which ended in a 1-1 draw last year, Football Kenya Federation was fined Sh1 million after dignitaries, led by deputy President William Ruto and ODM leader Raila Odinga accessed the playing arena at KasaraniEgypt's national team, the "Pharaohs" arrived in Nairobi on Tuesday night and held a training session under floodlights on Wednesday